The paper is about creating an ontology to make neural networks findable, accessible, interoperable, and reusable, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and deep learning (cs.DL). The paper also discusses the creation of a dataset and a search service, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE).
